vine.math.vector

Class Vec3f

  • java.lang.Object
    • vine.math.vector.Vec3f
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MutableVec3f

    public class Vec3f
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a immutable three-dimensional vector with single floating point precision.
    Author:
    Steffen Kromm, first created on 04.05.2016
